{"tid":1303023,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呼籲大家打電話去滙豐要求抽起TVB廣告","createTime":"2019-07-10T07:00:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T09:52:18.000Z","uid":41622,"like":72,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"a4bab7ecc4f2b6d85892cb69baf8ccc83862136f","tid":1303023,"uid":41622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T07:00:31.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">據聞 (friend講) 滙豐依家統計緊有幾多客投訴喺TVB落廣告！<br />\n<br />\n大家用緊滙豐就快啲走去投訴啦！<br />\n<br />\n網頁<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hsbc.com.hk/zh-hk/personal/help-and-support/contact-hsbc/form.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hsbc.com.hk%2Fzh-hk%2Fpersonal%2Fhelp-and-support%2Fcontact-hsbc%2Fform.html&d=q18Y%2F9yBacX5GGPSgvrSC72U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=5754a57e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hsbc.com.hk/zh-hk/personal/help-and-support/contact-hsbc/form.html</a><br />\n<br />\n電郵<br />\ndfv.enquiry@hsbc.com.hk<br />\n<br />\n電話 (是但打一個)<br />\n一般客戶：2233 3000 (quick key: 1-5-#-0)<br />\n運籌理財：2748 8333 (quick key: 1-5-#-0)<br />\n卓越理財：2233 3322 (quick key: 1-0-#-4-3)<br />\nCollect call：+852 2233 3388 (quick key: 1)<br />\n<br />\n打通咗要表明你係滙豐嘅客戶<br />\n點稱呼你 (最好留姓氏)<br />\n之後投訴<br />\n要唔要書面回覆可以自己決定<br />\n<br />\n投訴內容 (小弟文筆唔好大家自己加下嘢)<br />\n因應TVB對近日示威嘅報導失實，要求滙豐抽起喺TVB嘅廣告，以表示不滿。<br />\n</span></strong>"},{"pid":"e8800b4e2e0145a0672e334df7a6755412dd5448","tid":1303023,"uid":166117,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T07:02:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FbGvyqe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFbGvyqe.png&h=d8147e40&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EYXCdqf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEYXCdqf.png&h=3fab917f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1db89cee868ace0bff520ea4c038ee2e3adc26cb","tid":1303023,"uid":41622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T07:03:03.000Z","msg":"push